data.description: Find your new home in the Von Elm edition in Yukon! Great curb appeal! Large bedrooms, master has huge walk-in closet, over-sized utility room, updated large kitchen with plenty of cabinet and counter space, large living with woodburning fireplace, and huge dining area perfect for entertaining! Updated granite throughout the entire home. Covered back patio. Located just minutes from the Turnpike and lots of shopping and places to eat. Don't miss out on this Yukon gem!
